    a: "Yes, any time. In your profile, under 'Privacy & data', hit 'Download my data' and we generate a file with all your info on the spot. If you prefer email, write to " + siteConfig.contactEmail + " and we reply within 30 days max. It is a right recognized by GDPR and equivalent laws.",
  },
  {
    q: "Can I use the app offline?",
    a: "Not today. The app is 100% web. The next steps in our plan include turning it into a PWA (installable on mobile) and later a native app.",
  },
  {
    q: "Do you delete my account if I ask?",
    a: "Yes. No need to email us: from your profile, under 'Privacy & data', there's a red 'Delete my account' button. Your profile, reviews, photos and balances vanish from the app immediately and backup copies are purged within 30 days max. Before deleting, from the same section you can download a full copy of your data. We only keep aggregated anonymous stats and the technical logs the law requires.",
  },
  {
    q: "Do you pay real money for peanuts?",
    a: "No. Peanuts are a symbolic internal currency. They cannot be bought, sold or redeemed for money outside the app.",
  },
  {
    q: "Do you sell or share my data with third parties?",
    a: "No. We never sell data and we do not share it for advertising. We only share it with strictly necessary providers (database, hosting, emails), under contract and solely to deliver the service.",
  },
  {
    q: "How do I change my email?",
    a: "From 'Profile → Security → Change email'. Type the new address, we send a confirmation link there, and once you click it the change is live. Don't worry: your peanuts, tickets, reviews and badges are tied to your account (not to the email), so nothing is lost when you switch.",
  },
  {
    q: "How do I download a coloring sheet?",
    a: "On the 'Coloring Corner' page. Each download costs 1 peanut 🥜 (earned for free by sharing, by your daily streak, or by approved reviews).",
  },
  {
    q: "How do I submit a book review?",
    a: "Go to 'Reviews' in the menu, pick the book, upload a cover photo + at least 1 interior photo, set your rating (1–5 stars) and, optionally, a comment. Then it goes through moderation.",
  },
  {
    q: "How do I unsubscribe from the newsletter?",
    a: "Every email has an 'Unsubscribe' link at the bottom. One click is enough. We do not ask for reasons or extra confirmations.",
  },
  {
    q: "How does the daily streak work?",
    a: "If you visit the app at least once a day, your streak goes up. Keeping it earns you +2 peanuts per day. If you miss a day, it resets to 1 (unless you have a streak freeze available).",
  },
  {
    q: "How does the monthly giveaway work?",
    a: "Every month we give away 1 free physical book. Every approved review earns you 5 tickets 🎟️, and you can buy more with peanuts (3 🥜 = 1 ticket). The draw runs automatically on day 1 of each month and we notify the winner by email.",
  },
  {
    q: "How do peanuts 🥜 work?",
    a: "They are our in-app currency. Earned FOR FREE (sharing, daily streak, reviews) and spent on cosmetic or useful things (badges, boosts, downloads, tickets). They never cost real money. They cannot be bought and cannot be redeemed for cash.",
  },
  {
    q: "How long until my review is approved?",
    a: "We aim to moderate in under 48 hours. When it is approved you receive an email and your 5 tickets are automatically credited to your account.",
  },
  {
    q: "Is there an age limit to create an account?",
    a: "Yes. The account is managed by an adult aged 18 or over (parent, grandparent, legal guardian). You confirm this with a checkbox at sign-up. The little ones in the family can read the books, color, and join in with you, but the account always stays under the responsible adult. If we find an account being managed by a minor without an adult behind it, we delete it.",
  },
  {
    q: "Is the app free?",
    a: "Yes. Registering, posting reviews, downloading free artwork, entering the monthly giveaway and earning peanuts is 100% free. Physical books are bought on Amazon; that happens off our app.",
  },
  {
    q: "My review was rejected — what now?",
